  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc7\u0b95 \u0baa\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Exclusive transport service for school students",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Initially, 40 buses will be put into service in the Upper Province from the first of next month.",
        "Only teachers and students can travel in these buses, said the Executive Director of the National Transport Commission, Nilan Mirundapa.",
        "He mentioned the above while attending the press conference held at the Government Information Department on 29th.",
        "Considering the welfare of the students, the National Transport Council has decided to start the 'Transport Service for Students' in the first phase of the Upper Province while the educational activities of the school students are affected due to fuel shortage.",
        "This project will be carried out in collaboration with the Upper Provincial Urban Development Authority and the Ministry of Transport. This project will be started as a public school service. Normal bus fare will be collected from the students.",
        "40 buses will be put into service under this project from the first of next month in the Upper Province.",
        "This program will be carried out for the benefit of the students of the main schools in the Colombo district, Kambaha, Kalutara, Horana, Homagama and Mahakarama and their neighboring schools.",
        "In order to identify these buses, the slogan 'Public School Service' will be affixed on the buses. Also, more information can be obtained through the emergency telephone number 1955. Information can be obtained by accessing the official website of the National Transport Council.",
        "These buses will travel to the school at 07.30 a.m. and will resume service after school is over. These buses will be fully monitored. Only students and teachers of schools can use this service, he said."
      ],
